modName: Cubic Hairs for Females for Unique Bodies by Race
summary:
With this mod you can add pubic hairs for females for working vaginas.
It uses the SOS-Addon-Script and the Hair works on Slot 52
each race can use a specific body, only Khajiit and Argonian will get no hair.
descriptionHtml:
[b][size=4][b][size=4][size=3][color=#ff7700][size=5]ï»¿Cubic Hairs for Females for Unique Bodies by Race[/size][/color]

[/size][/size][/size][/b][/size][/b][size=4][size=4][size=3][size=4]This Mod uses[/size][/size] the SOS-Addon-Script and adds Female Pubic-Hairs for working vaginas.
Each race from the Unique Bodies by Race will get body specific formed pubic hairs except Argonian and Khajiit-Females.

The following hair-styles are available[/size][/size][b][size=4][b][size=4]

[/size][/b][/size][/b][size=4][size=4]Khajiit and Argonian-Females won't get any hair.

What you have to do:

1. Generate the hairs for your desired bodytypes

Choose the group in bodyslide[/size][/size][b][size=4][b][size=4]
ï»¿[img]data:image/png;base64,[/img]

[/size][/b][/size][/b][size=4][size=4]Select your disered preset[/size][/size][b][size=4][b][size=4]
ï»¿[img]data:image/png;base64,[/img]

[/size][/b][/size][/b][size=4][size=4]Activate "Build Morphs"[/size][/size][b][size=4][b][size=4]
[img]data:image/png;base64,[/img]

[/size][/b][/size][/b][size=4][size=4]Klick "Batch Build..."[/size][/size][b][size=4][b][size=4]
[img]data:image/png;base64,[/img]

[/size][/b][/size][/b][size=4][size=4]Make shure everything is selected, then klick "Build"[/size][/size][b][size=4][b][size=4]
ï»¿[img]data:image/png;base64,[/img]

[/size][/b][/size][/b][size=4][size=4]Copy the generated files to the according target directory of the Unique Bodies by Race folder:[/size][/size][b][size=4][b][size=4]
ï»¿[img]data:image/png;base64,[/img]

[/size][/b][/size][/b][size=4][size=4]%Modnamefolder%>meshes>actors>character>%Racename%>SOS>Cubic Hair for Females[/size][/size][b][size=4][b][size=4]
ï»¿[img]data:image/png;base64,[/img]


[/size][/b][/size][/b][size=4][size=4]Now there is ab bit work to do.
Open each nif-file with nifskope and edit the NiStringExtraData folder to
[size=4][size=4]actors\character\%Racename%\SOS\Cubic Hair for Females[/size][/size]
and save the nif-file[/size][/size][b][size=4][b][size=4]
ï»¿[img]data:image/png;base64,[/img]

[size=5]SLOT USAGE and CONFLICT[/size]

[/size][/b][/size][/b][size=4][size=4][size=4]The hairs use slot 52.

As such it will conflict with any armor mod piece that uses that slot.[/size][/size][/size][b][size=4][b][size=4]


[size=5]REQUIREMENTS[/size]

[/size][/b][/size][/b][size=4][size=4]ï»¿Female Body Replacer (I use the Cosio4.0 HD Body, but it should work with uunp-bodies as well)

Schlongs of Skyrim

Unique Bodies by Race

Cubic Hairs Renewal for CBBE and UUNP

Bodyslide 2.0 and Outfit Studio.[/size][/size][b][size=4][b][size=4]
